Class FacebookUser

  • java.lang.Object
    • socialmedia.User
      • facebook.FacebookUser

  • public class FacebookUser
extends User
    This class is an extension of the User class. The variables added here are the facebook exclusive fields for a user. Can represent a Facebook User, Page or Group.
    See Also:
    User
